- **蛻､譁ｭ譌･譎・*: 2026-05-13
- **閭梧勹**: CS-7 amendment 縺ｧ N=3 multi_lora_3 縺ｯ M9-C-adopt scope 縺ｨ
  defer縲Ｔpike 縺ｧ single_lora vs no_lora 縺ｮ縺ｿ螳滓ｸｬ縲・odex HIGH-3 縺・  "mock-first + real-after benchmark is necessary but not enough if it
  only runs a short CS-7 harness" + churn diagnostic 蠢・ｦ√→謖・遭縲・- **豎ｺ螳・*:
  - **A-4a (mock-first縲￣hase D)**: CS-7 4 trigger NON-FIRE 蠢・・(迴ｾ迥ｶ
    邯ｭ謖・縲Ｎock_nietzsche_r8 + mock_rikyu_r8 繧・`tools/spike/build_mock_lora.py`
    縺ｧ逕滓・
  - **A-4b (real-after縲￣hase E)**: HIGH-3 churn diagnostic 霑ｽ蜉
    - **steady-state metric** (CS-7 諡｡蠑ｵ): TTFT p50/p95/p99 / ITL
      p50/p95/p99 / e2e p99 / output tok/s / error rate
    - **churn diagnostic** (譁ｰ隕上？IGH-3):
