| **II (no reversal)** | Vendi point >= matched baseline OR CI spans 0 OR Burrows reduction <= 0 OR CI spans 0 | LoRA failure 縺・live hypothesis 縺ｮ縺ｾ縺ｾ縲〉etrain v2 蠢・ｦ・|
| **III (mixed)** | Vendi / Burrows 縺ｮ迚・婿縺ｮ縺ｿ reverse縲√∪縺溘・ rank-mixed direction縲√∪縺溘・ thresholds 驛ｨ蛻・clear | 荳｡蝗蟄仙ｯ・ｸ弱〉etrain v2 + multi-turn protocol fix 縺ｮ combination 蠢・ｦ・|
| **IV (no information gain)** | 謗｡蜿・fail (>= 1 shard 縺ｧ focal_observed < 0.9 ﾃ・focal_target) OR 蜈ｨ rank 縺ｧ CI width > 1.5ﾃ・single-turn pilot CI width | identifiability 荳崎・縺ｮ縺ｾ縺ｾ縲￣hase E A-6 7500-turn 縺悟髪荳縺ｮ closure path |

