### 謗｡逕ｨ spec (DA-9 amendment縲∬ｩｳ邏ｰ縺ｯ `feature/m9-c-adopt-retrain-v2-design/design-final.md` ﾂｧ3)

1. **baseline backend**: no-LoRA SGLang multi-turn 繧・primary baseline
   (Ollama 縺ｯ historical reference 縺ｮ縺ｿ)
2. **`min_examples` 繧・quality proxy 縺ｨ縺励※謾ｾ譽・* (MEDIUM-6 + Step 1
   evidence; `realised_examples=5022` 譌｢縺ｫ SLO 1000 縺ｮ 5x)縲・   `realised_examples` 繧・post-weighting 縺ｧ 3,000 floor 邯ｭ謖・(operational
   SLO縲〈uality proof 縺ｧ縺ｯ縺ｪ縺・
3. **per-example signal weighting** (clamped `[0.1, 3.0]`縲［ean=1.0 縺ｫ
   normalised):
   ```
   weight = lang_factor   * 0.35     # de=1.4, en=1.0, mixed=0.5, ja=0.2
          + length_factor * 0.20     # <30=0.3 / 30-59=0.8 / 60-119=1.5 / 120+=2.0
          + monolog_bonus * 0.15     # addressee=None 竊・1.5, else 1.0
          + marker_factor * 0.30     # max(density/2.0, 0.2)
   ```
   coefficients 縺ｯ **heuristic (NOT empirical)** 縺ｧ縲（nterpretable 縺ｪ
   sum-to-1 weighting縲Ｕraining kickoff 逶ｴ蜑阪↓ `weight-audit.json` 繧貞・蜉・   (per-language weighted mass / top 5% weight share / N_eff = (ﾎ｣w)ﾂｲ/ﾎ｣wﾂｲ)
4. **WeightedTrainer** (HF Trainer.compute_loss override) 繧定・蜑榊ｮ溯｣・
   token CE `reduction="none"` 竊・per-example mean over non-`-100` labels 竊・   `(per_example_loss * weight).sum() / weight.sum().clamp_min(eps)`縲・F
   Trainer 縺ｮ `sample_weight` 閾ｪ蜍・consume 縺ｫ縺ｯ萓晏ｭ倥＠縺ｪ縺・5. **Group-aware validation split** (training kickoff 縺ｮ譛蛻・: 5,022
   examples 繧・`(source_shard, dialog_id)` 縺ｧ group 蛹悶・0/10 random split
   (seed=42縲《tratified by `source_shard_type`)縲・*eval split 縺ｫ monolog
   re-cast 縺ｯ蜷ｫ繧√↑縺・*
6. **Monolog re-cast diversity injection**: training group 縺ｮ natural
   shards 縺九ｉ Kant 騾｣邯・2 turn 繧・`addressee=None` 縺ｧ邨仙粋縲×150-300
   synthetic monolog examples 繧定ｿｽ蜉縲Ａsynthetic_source_dialog_id` +
   `synthetic_source_turn_indices` metadata 莉倅ｸ弱・   `assert len(set(train_dialog_ids) & set(eval_dialog_ids)) == 0`
7. **rank=8 蝗ｺ螳・* (DA-12 provisional carry-over)縲￣EFT setup PR #163 K-ﾎｲ
   baseline 蜷御ｸ (`target_modules=[q,k,v,o_proj]`, `lora_alpha=16`,
   `lora_dropout=0.05`, NF4 + double quant)
8. **max_steps 2000 竊・4000** (weighted batch 縺ｮ effective LR scaling)
9. **eval batch=1 + loss-only eval** (VRAM 謚大宛縲？IGH-B 蜿肴丐)
10. **Candidate C (targeted hybrid) fallback**: weight-concentration audit
    縺ｧ N_eff <1000 or top-5% weight share 竕･50%縲＾R DA-14 4 霆ｸ REJECT縲＾R
    overfit diagnostics 蜈・・竊・+2,500 turn 繧・**de/en ﾃ・竕･60 token ﾃ・    monolog/long-form** 縺ｧ targeted 謗｡蜿悶＠縺ｦ蜀・training

