| Burrows reduction | 竕･ 10% | **竕･ 5%** point + CI lower > 0 | literature shoulder 5-15% (Burrows 1987 / Eder 2016)縲∫樟迥ｶ LoRA effect proper -0.83% (wrong direction) 縺ｪ縺ｮ縺ｧ 5% pass 縺ｯ逵溘・ shift 繧呈э蜻ｳ |
| ICC primary | ICC(C,k) 竕･ 0.6 | **ICC(A,1) 竕･ 0.55** point + CI lower 竕･ 0.50 | ICC(C,k) >0.97 縺ｧ saturated 竊・diagnostic 縺ｫ譬ｼ荳九￡縲！CC(A,1) 縺ｯ no-LoRA SGLang baseline 縺ｧ 0.9061 / LoRA-on r=8 縺ｧ 0.9002 縺ｧ persona-fit shift 縺瑚ｦｳ貂ｬ蜿ｯ閭ｽ縺ｪ蟶ｯ蝓・|
| throughput | 竕･ 70% baseline | **竕･ 70%** 荳榊､・| DA-1 縺ｨ蜷・|

