.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:796:## DA-13 — DA-12 identifiability empirical follow-up (multi-turn pilot investigation 第 1 セッション 2026-05-14)
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:804:- **背景**: DA-12 verdict = DEFER で identifiability 不能と認定された 2 因子
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:826:**Scenario thresholds**:
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:830:| **I (reversal confirmed)** | Vendi Δ point < 0 AND CI upper < 0 AND Cohen's d < -0.5 AND Burrows reduction point > 5% AND CI lower > 0 AND >= 1 sister rank in same direction (Vendi + Burrows 両軸) | historical baseline-like no-prior multi-turn sampling protocol が pilot direction を反転させるのに十分 → methodology confound が dominant な候補 |
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:831:| **II (no reversal)** | Vendi point >= matched baseline OR CI spans 0 OR Burrows reduction <= 0 OR CI spans 0 | LoRA failure が live hypothesis のまま、retrain v2 必要 |
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:832:| **III (mixed)** | Vendi / Burrows の片方のみ reverse、または rank-mixed direction、または thresholds 部分 clear | 両因子寄与、retrain v2 + multi-turn protocol fix の combination 必要 |
.steering/20260513-m9-c-adopt/decisions.md:833:| **IV (no information gain)** | 採取 fail (>= 1 shard で focal_observed < 0.9 × focal_target) OR 全 rank で CI width > 1.5× single-turn pilot CI width | identifiability 不能のまま、Phase E A-6 7500-turn が唯一の closure path |
